SUMMARY:Volunteer at CUMAC (CUMAC)
DESCRIPTION:Come help sort food to be distributed to families in our communities experiencing hunger.  WE will travel together to and from the church. We have 4 spots available for High School youth\, who can get credit for Community Service!!  Sign up is first come\, first serve. \n  \nIf you have any questions or need more information about any of these events\, please contact Rev. Leah at: \nEmail: lmccullough@unioncng.org
