SUMMARY:Women's Breakfast (Assembly Room)
DESCRIPTION:It’s Game Day! \nGet ready for a morning of fast-paced fun! At our next breakfast\, April 18\, at 9:00 am\, we’ll be rolling the dice for a few rounds of “Bunco.” This game is easy to learn and relies entirely on luck. The winners of each round move to a different card table. It’s a fantastic way to say hi to everyone. \nCome join us for a wonderful breakfast with friends. Please RSVP to Karen Ermler\, karen.ermler@gmail.com if you plan to attend. \nGuests are always welcome.
URL:https://www.unioncong.org/event/womens-breakfast-assembly-room-4-2/
LOCATION:Assembly Room
CATEGORIES:All Church Events,All Events,Featured Events,Small Groups
